{{Vgname|神奇的阿力|en=Amazing Alex|cn=神奇的阿力|tw=神奇的艾力克斯}}是一款由开发过《[[愤怒的小鸟|愤怒的小鸟]]》<ref>{{Cite web| url= http://www.rovio.com/en/our-work/games| title= Our Work| accessdate= 2013-05-03| language= en| archive-date= 2015-12-13| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151213093103/http://www.rovio.com/en/our-work/games| dead-url= no}}</ref>的[[Rovio娱乐|Rovio娱乐]]公司开发的物理类[[益智游戏|益智游戏]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://yle.fi/uutiset/new_amazing_alex_game_chases_angry_birds/6091544|title=Amazing Alex|access-date=2012-07-18|archive-date=2016-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160504223542/http://yle.fi/uutiset/new_amazing_alex_game_chases_angry_birds/6091544|dead-url=no}}</ref>这款游戏最初由Rovio的CEO在芬兰[[Yle|Yle]]电视台早间节目中提及。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://areena.yle.fi/tv/1547595 |title=Ylen aamu-tv: Vieraana Angry Birdsejä johtava Mikael Hed (video clip in Finnish) |accessdate=2012-07-18 |archive-date=2014-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112235838/http://areena.yle.fi/tv/1547595 |dead-url=no }}</ref>这一游戏的原型是由Noel Llopis（Snappy Touch）与Miguel Ángel Friginal（Mystery Coconut）开发的[[Casey's_Contraptions|Casey's Contraptions]]，后来被Rovio收购。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/170084/Rovio_confirms_acquisition_of_Caseys_Contraptions_IP.php |title= Rovio acquires Casey's Contraptions |access-date= 2012-07-18 |archive-date= 2021-03-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210303121753/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/170084/Rovio_confirms_acquisition_of_Caseys_Contraptions_IP.php |dead-url= no }}</ref>

== 背景 ==

游戏的背景是一位对事物充满好奇的男孩[[艾力克斯|艾力克斯]]，他拥有无边无际的想像力<ref>{{Cite web| url= http://down.tech.sina.com.cn/3gsoft/download.php?id=7819| title= 神奇的阿力 Amazing Alex| accessdate= 2013-05-03| language= zh| archive-date= 2016-03-04| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304192756/http://down.tech.sina.com.cn/3gsoft/download.php?id=7819| dead-url= no}}</ref>，喜歡通过摆弄周围的物品，產生连锁反应的装置，来达到任务目标。<ref>{{cite video| date = 2012-07-10| title = Amazing Alex official launch trailer| url = http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xk7vezL36IU| publisher = Amazing Alex official launch trailer| accessdate = 2013-03-29| archive-date = 2022-01-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220117123018/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xk7vezL36IU| dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 玩法 ==

這遊戲要利用各種的道具，透過连锁反应的装置，產生物理現象，達到過關的條件，只要你順利達成，就會到下一關。如果在過關的同時能碰觸到那些星星，會有更高的分數。遊戲要先將道具和物品做適當的擺設，等一切都設置妥當後，按開始鍵，物品就會開始運作了。<ref>{{Cite web| url= http://www.freegroup.org/2012/08/free-android-apps-amazing-alex/#.UVTyrhynr9w| title= [Android] Amazing Alex 憤怒鳥團隊最新力作，透過各種物理作用來玩遊戲！| accessdate= 2013-03-29| author= Boring| date= 2012-08-14| publisher= 免費資源網路社群| language= zh| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130328144458/http://www.freegroup.org/2012/08/free-android-apps-amazing-alex/#.UVTyrhynr9w| archive-date= 2013-03-28| dead-url= yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite video| date = 2012-07-15| title = Amazing Alex - Level 3-1 - Walkthrough - 3 Stars| url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yGciq9zu_UI| publisher = i3Stars| accessdate = 2013-03-29| time = 0:35| archive-date = 2016-03-16| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160316160404/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yGciq9zu_UI| dead-url = no}}</ref>

玩家也可自行使用各種的道具設計關卡，<ref>{{Cite web| url= http://www.soft4fun.net/ipad-iphone/amazing-alex.htm| title= 「Amazing Alex」Angry Birds 公司最新力作強勢登場！| accessdate= 2013-03-29| author= Werboy| date= 2012-07-13| publisher= 硬是要學| language= zh| quote= 如果你已經玩出一些心得的話，還可以自己設計關卡來跟世界玩家分享、挑戰，也就是說有無限個關卡等你去挑戰，不錯吧！| archive-date= 2013-04-10| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130410172035/http://www.soft4fun.net/ipad-iphone/amazing-alex.htm| dead-url= no}}</ref>也可以把自行設計的關卡分享出去<ref>{{cite encyclopedia| encyclopedia = Amazing Alex Wiki| title = User created levels| url = http://amazingalex.wikia.com/wiki/User_created_levels| accessdate = 2013-05-03| quote = One of the great featues of Amazing Alex the the ability to create and share your levels.| language = en| archive-date = 2016-03-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305152138/http://amazingalex.wikia.com/wiki/User_created_levels| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 外界評價 ==

此遊戲可透過[[App_Store|App Store]]的[[Game_Center|Game Center]]分享自己的遊戲流程，有玩家認為此舉可增加遊戲的耐玩性。<ref>{{Cite web| url= http://techorange.com/2012/08/03/amazing-alex/| title= 能否拷貝憤怒鳥經驗？談 Rovio 新作 Amazing Alex| accessdate= 2013-03-29| author= 唐比爾| date= 2012-08-03| publisher= 科技報橘| language= zh| quote= 利用社群及分享的概念，增加遊戲耐玩性| archive-date= 2014-08-19| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140819202209/http://techorange.com/2012/08/03/amazing-alex/| dead-url= no}}</ref>另外，有玩家認為《神奇的阿力》是一款寓教於樂的遊戲。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://playpcesor.blogspot.com/2012/07/amazing-alex.html |title=Amazing Alex 憤怒鳥團隊新作下載！神奇的物理益智遊戲 |accessdate=2013-05-03 |author=異塵行者 |publisher=電腦玩物 |quote=「Amazing Alex」是一款寓教於樂，物體動態效果精采的好遊戲，推薦大家可以玩玩看。 |archive-date=2013-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130307194439/http://playpcesor.blogspot.com/2012/07/amazing-alex.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在網站[[Pocket_Gamer|Pocket Gamer]]中，有玩家指出，把《神奇的阿力》和《[[憤怒的小鳥|憤怒的小鳥]]》相比，後者較好：“我並不是說《神奇的阿力》不是一種上癮的體驗 - 它只是和憤怒的小鳥相比，有較少的刺激感。當你完成一個關卡，你很少把你的手臂扔在空中。”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/Android/Amazing+Alex/review.asp?c=43021&srch=Amazing+Alex |title=Amazing Alex |accessdate=2013-05-04 |author=Harry Slater |language=en |quote=That's not to say that Amazing Alex isn't an addictive experience - it's just that compared to Angry Birds, there's less excitement involved. You rarely feel like throwing your arms in the air when you've completed a puzzle, for example, and the absence of any kind of antagonist reduces the stakes slightly. |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304193608/http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/Android/Amazing+Alex/review.asp?c=43021&srch=Amazing+Alex |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在[[Google_Play|Google Play]]中，該遊戲的平均分數是4.3分（滿分5分）。有玩家在[[Google_Play|Google Play]]上批評，《神奇的阿力》並不是太有趣。

